{"id":"6573","name":"happy-hour-true-colors","title":"Happy Hour: True Colors","author":"Christy Frink","date":"2011-02-17T17:30:00-06:00","tags":[],"categories":["News"],"contentEncoded":"<div id=\"greet_block\"><noscript><div class=\"greet_block wpgb_cornered\"><div class=\"greet_text\"><div class=\"greet_image\"><a href=\"http://nashvillest.com/feed/rss/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"http://nashvillest.com/wp-content/plugins/wp-greet-box/images/rss_icon.png\" alt=\"WP Greet Box icon\"></a></div>Hello there! If you are new here, you might want to <a href=\"http://nashvillest.com/feed/rss/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>subscribe to the RSS feed</strong></a> for updates on this topic.<div style=\"clear:both\"></div><div class=\"greet_block_powered_by\">Powered by <a href=\"http://omninoggin.com/projects/wordpress-plugins/wp-greet-box-wordpress-plugin/\" title=\"WP Greet Box WordPress Plugin\" style=\"text-decoration:none;\">WP Greet Box</a> <a href=\"http://omninoggin.com/\" title=\"WordPress Plugin\" style=\"text-decoration:none;\">WordPress Plugin</a></div><div style=\"clear:both\"></div></div></div></noscript></div><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/juniperberry/5452460414/in/pool-715021@N24/\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.flickr.com&apos;]);\"><img class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"http://farm5.static.flickr.com/4093/5452460414_b1e65b905b.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"375\"></a></p><ul><li>Metro is trying to go after the folks who put up signs on the side of the road or on utility poles by proposing a $50 fine for the offense. [<a href=\"http://www.newschannel5.com/story/14045634/city-leaders-launch-campaign-to-get-rid-of-roadside-signs\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.newschannel5.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">WTVF</a>]</li><li>The University of the South is doing the unfathomable: <em>Cutting</em> tuition by 10%. [<a href=\"http://www.wsmv.com/education/26900083/detail.html\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.wsmv.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">WSMV</a>]</li><li>Congratulations, Nashville! You&#x2019;re the fourth brainiest city in the country according to Forbes, behind New Orleans, Raleigh and Austin. [<a href=\"http://www.wsmv.com/health/26901392/detail.html\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.wsmv.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">WSMV</a>]</li><li>The road closures around the Music City Center construction are just going on and on and on&#x2026; [<a href=\"http://www.wkrn.com/Global/story.asp?S=14048349\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.wkrn.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">WKRN</a>]</li><li>City officials are holding a public meeting to discuss the very bleak Sidewalk Situation in Green Hills. [<a href=\"http://www.wsmv.com/community/26904316/detail.html\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.wsmv.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">WSMV</a>]</li><li>The Nashville Area Chamber of Commerce is concerned about the fact that Metro Schools&#x2019; ACT numbers are &#x201C;essentially unacceptably low.&#x201D; [<a href=\"http://wpln.org/?p=24255\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;wpln.org&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">WPLN</a>]</li><li>We&#x2019;re about two weeks away from a potential football lockout and both the players&#x2019; union and the NFL have agreed to try some mediation as a last-ditch effort to prevent that from happening. [<a href=\"http://www.wkrn.com/Global/story.asp?S=14051787\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.wkrn.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">WKRN</a>]</li></ul><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><em>Photo by </em><a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/juniperberry/5452460414/in/pool-715021@N24/\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.flickr.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\"><em>jcbonbon</em></a>.</p><p>Related posts:<ol><li><a href=\"http://nashvillest.com/2011/02/22/happy-hour-true-blood/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Permanent Link: Happy Hour: True Blood\">Happy Hour: True Blood</a></li></ol></p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<!--END .entry-content .article-->"}